@page "/TextArea/Default-Functionalities"

@using Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs

@*Hidden:Lines*@
@inherits SampleBaseComponent
@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager


@*End:Hidden*@

<SampleDescription>
    <p>This example demonstrates the default functionalities of the <a href='https://www.syncfusion.com/blazor-components/blazor-textbox/' target='_blank' aria-label="TextBox">TextArea</a> component. Type a character in the TextBox element or focus-in to the TextBox for floating the label text. The label will be positioned back to TextBox on focus-out without value.</p>
</SampleDescription>
<ActionDescription>
    <p>TextAreas are the input elements that allow to get input from the user. It allows the user either to edit or display the input values.</p><br>
    <p><b>Outlined & Filled Textarea :</b></p>
    <p>You can render the following two types of text fields in the material theme by adding <b>e-outline</b> and <b>e-filled</b> class to <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_CssClass' target='_blank' aria-label="CssClass">CssClass</a> API.
        <ul>
            <li>Filled text fields</li>
            <li>Outlined text fields</li>
        </ul>
    </p>
    <p><b>Floating Label :</b></p>
    <p>The floating label textarea floats the label above the textarea after focusing or filling with value in the textarea. You can create the floating label textarea by using the <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_FloatLabelType' target='_blank' aria-label="FloatLabelType">FloatLabelType</a> API.
        <ul>
            <li><b>Never</b> - The placeholder text should never float.</li>
            <li><b>Always</b> - The placeholder text floats above the textarea always.</li>
            <li><b>Auto</b> - The placeholder text floats above the textarea while focusing or entering a value in the textarea.</li>
        </ul>
    </p>
    <p><b>RTL TextArea : </b></p>
    <p>You can render the textarea in right to left direction by enabling the <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_EnableRtl' target='_blank' aria-label="EnableRtl">EnableRtl</a> API.</p>
    <p><b>Disabled TextArea : </b></p>
    <p>You can render the textarea with disabled state using <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_Enabled' target='_blank' aria-label="Enabled">Enabled</a> API.</p>
    <p><b>Readonly TextArea : </b></p>
    <p>You can render the readonly textarea by enabling <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_Readonly' target='_blank' aria-label="Readonly">Readonly</a> API.</p>
    <p><b>Validation states : </b></p>
    <p>You can apply the validation styles to the textarea by adding <b>e-success</b>, <b>e-warning</b>, <b>e-error</b> class to the <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_CssClass' target='_blank' aria-label="CssClass">CssClass</a> API.</p>
    <p><b>Sizing : </b></p>
    <p>You can render the textarea in a small size by adding <b>e-small</b>, <b>e-bigger</b> classes to the <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_CssClass' target='_blank' aria-label="CssClass">CssClass</a> API. Also, you can set the custom width to the textarea by using <a href='https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/blazor/Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.SfTextBox.html#Syncfusion_Blazor_Inputs_SfTextBox_Width' target='_blank'>Width</a> API.</p>      
    <p><b>See also</b></p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href='https://blazor.syncfusion.com/documentation/textbox/getting-started/' target='_blank' aria-label="Blazor TextBox Getting Started documentation">Getting started with Blazor TextArea</a></li>
    </ul>
</ActionDescription>

<div class="col-lg-12 control-section">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="row material">
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                <b class="example-label">Outlined and Filled</b>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row material">
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                <SfTextArea Placeholder="Outline" CssClass="e-outline" Width="100%" ResizeMode=Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.Resize.None
               FloatLabelType="FloatLabelType.Auto"></SfTextArea>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                <SfTextArea Placeholder="Filled" CssClass="e-filled" Width="100%" ResizeMode=Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.Resize.None
                    FloatLabelType="FloatLabelType.Auto"></SfTextArea>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                <b class="example-label">Modes</b>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                <SfTextArea FloatLabelType="@FloatLabelType.Auto" Width="100%" ResizeMode=Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.Resize.None Placeholder="Default"></SfTextArea>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                <SfTextArea Placeholder="RTL" FloatLabelType="@FloatLabelType.Auto" Width="100%" ResizeMode=Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.Resize.None EnableRtl="true"></SfTextArea>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                <b class="example-label">Validation States</b>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-lg-4 col-md-4">
                <SfTextArea Placeholder="Success" CssClass="e-success"
                            FloatLabelType="FloatLabelType.Auto" ResizeMode=Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.Resize.None Width="100%"></SfTextArea>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-lg-4 col-md-4">
                 <SfTextArea Placeholder="Warning" CssClass="e-warning"
                            FloatLabelType="FloatLabelType.Auto" ResizeMode=Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.Resize.None Width="100%"></SfTextArea>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-lg-4 col-md-4">
                 <SfTextArea Placeholder="Error" CssClass="e-error"
                            FloatLabelType="FloatLabelType.Auto" ResizeMode=Syncfusion.Blazor.Inputs.Resize.None Width="100%"></SfTextArea>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
